text.div:
ActIncidentCode

Set of codes indicating the type of incident or accident.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include codes from http://hl7.org/fhir/v3/ActCode where concept is-a _ActIncidentCode
  • Exclude these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/v3/ActCode
